data.description: This charming single-family home is situated in a quiet and friendly neighborhood in Hollywood, Florida. It features two bedrooms and two bathrooms, with a spacious living and dining area. Impact Windows and doors. The kitchen is equipped with an electric range, dishwasher, and refrigerator. The home also has a screened porch, a patio, and a fenced backyard for outdoor enjoyment, and plenty of room for a pool. The roof is made of barrel tiles, the flooring is oak wood and tiled throughout. Avocado banana tree.The home has a lot size of 7,799 square feet, 4 cars parking, and No HOA fees! It is close to top-rated schools, parks, shopping, Hospitals, and entertainment venues. Ft Laud Airport is 11 min drive, and MIAMI Airport is 34 Min Drive. Universities nearby LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION.
